metadata.name: Damavand
metadata.description:
Mount Damavand is a potentially active stratovolcano, the highest peak in Iran and Western Asia and the highest volcano in Asia and the second highest volcano in the Eastern Hemisphere, at an elavation of 5,609 meters. Damavand has a special place in Persian mythology and folkore.
Damavand is one of my favorite places to chill out since childhood. So many memories made me consider to make one of my 3D artwork videos as a time-lapse of Milky way around Damavand.
